# Machine Registry
#
# Maps machine IDs to friendly names for display in zsh prompt, Claude Code statusline, etc.
# Format: machine_id|name|emoji (emoji optional — auto-assigned from name hash if empty)
#
# Machine ID sources:
#   Linux: /etc/machine-id
#   macOS: IOPlatformUUID from ioreg
#
# Manage with: machine-register [name]
#              machine-register --list
#              machine-register --remove
